@document.meta
title: Inline React Test
@end

* Testing React Inlines

This is a counter component:

@inline react
<button onClick={() => setCount(c => c + 1)}>
  Count: {count}
</button>
@end

* Multiple Inlines

First inline:

@inline react
<div>Hello from React!</div>
@end

Second inline:

@inline react
<span>Goodbye from React!</span>
@end

* Content After Inlines

This text comes after the inlines.
